---
---
<section class="py-16 bg-brand-softBg border-b border-brand-border/30">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Plan Kajabi Automations Around the Customer Journey</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-textMain mb-6">We structure intelligent workflows using Kajabi's internal automation logic to handle repetitive tasks behind the scenes.</p>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 border border-brand-border/50 mb-8 shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4 border-b border-brand-border pb-2">The Core Logic Flow</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-20 font-bold text-slate-700 bg-slate-100 py-1 text-center rounded border border-slate-200 mr-4">WHEN</div>
              <div class="text-brand-textMain">The trigger occurs (e.g., Form submitted)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-20 font-bold text-brand-primary bg-blue-50 py-1 text-center rounded border border-blue-100 mr-4">THEN</div>
              <div class="text-brand-textMain">The resulting action fires (e.g., Grant Offer)</div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <div class="w-20 font-bold text-brand-secondary bg-green-50 py-1 text-center rounded border border-green-100 mr-4 text-xs flex items-center justify-center">ONLY IF</div>
              <div class="text-brand-textMain italic text-sm">Condition narrows execution (Advanced only)</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 italic">Note: Automation options, including Basic and Advanced Automations, depend on your specific Kajabi plan, feature version, and account configuration.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">Our Delivery Process</h3>
        <ol class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mt-0.5">1</div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-brand-navy block">Map the customer and learner journey</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain mt-1">We identify where automated touchpoints are actually needed.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mt-0.5">2</div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-brand-navy block">Identify triggers and define actions</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain mt-1">Connecting forms, email activity, offers, purchases, courses, quizzes, and tags to specific resulting events.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mt-0.5">3</div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-brand-navy block">Add conditions where available</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain mt-1">Using 'Only If' filters to segment actions based on user behavior (requires Advanced Automations).</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mt-0.5">4</div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-brand-navy block">Test with controlled user accounts</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain mt-1">Verifying tags, email connections, and access grants before launch.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm mt-0.5">5</div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-brand-navy block">Document the final flow</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-textMain mt-1">Providing a clear record of the business logic driving your platform.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
